txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Monstrous wings from the bats near Gath Forthnír. Deilvery of the items should be made to Areneth at the hidden Ranger-outpost.
'We will find a use for this.'
'We can use the wings of bats as a way to alert others of dangers in this wild. Get them for us.'
Council of the North Task: Monstrous Wings
The Rangers at Gath Forthnír await a delivery of monstrous wings to be made to Areneth.
Deliver the monstrous wings to Areneth at Gath Forthnír in Angmar
You have accepted a task to collect and deliver monstrous wings from the bats near Gath Forthnír to Areneth at the hidden Ranger-camp.
Wanted: Monstrous wings from the bats near Gath Forthnír.
